last_episode_to_air.name: Grandma CatRat
last_episode_to_air.overview: CatRat wants everything to be perfect for his grandma's visit. But when things don't go as planned, the day is full of new and exciting surprises.

name: Gabby's Dollhouse
overview: This colorful series leads preschoolers room to room through a fantastical dollhouse of delightful mini-worlds and irresistible kitty characters.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: Cute cats, quirky crafts and colorful magic! Join kitty enthusiast Gabby and her sidekick Pandy Paws as they team up for a series of animated adventures.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: More paws-itively purr-fect fun awaits as Gabby and her dollhouse friends find new ways to learn, create and celebrate in a whimsical world of joy.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Gabby, Pandy and their crew of kitty friends are back with even more special deliveries, surprising journeys and make-at-home lessons, too!

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: New lessons, new surprises, same adorable kitties — including Floyd! Gabby leads the way with Pandy, CatRat, Cakey, Baby Box and other beloved pals.

seasons.name: Season 5
seasons.overview: From the Cat-osphere to Cat-O-Ween, Gabby, Pandy and pals mix their kitty magic and curiosity together to discover new adventures and ways to play!

seasons.name: Season 6
seasons.overview: Join Gabby, Pandy and their kitty pals for more creative adventures in their magical dollhouse, where they play dress-up, become superheroes and more!

seasons.name: Season 7
seasons.overview: Gabby and her best pal Pandy Paws meet fairies, find treasure and go on wild adventures inside her super-special dollhouse. Come play and sing along!

seasons.name: Season 8
seasons.overview: With all new songs and all new friends, the fun times never end for Gabby and her cute cat, Pandy Paws. Want to come along? It's time to get tiny!

seasons.name: Season 9
seasons.overview: With a pinch on her left and a pinch on her right, Gabby shrinks down for more kitty adventures in her super-cool dollhouse. Come and play along!

seasons.name: Season 10
seasons.overview: Come celebrate special holidays with Gabby and her friends, from a birthday to Family Day to Opposite Day. Every day is a celebration at the Dollhouse!

episodes.name: Spaceship
episodes.overview: Gabby and Pandy unbox their first surprise, show off their shrinking skills and take to the dollhouse for a meowt-of-this-world mission.

episodes.name: Gabby Gets the Hiccups
episodes.overview: It’s time for another dollhouse delivery! Gabby and Pandy share their new Meow Meow Mail with Cakey and work on a cure for a sneaky case of hiccups.

episodes.name: Hamster Kitties
episodes.overview: A fuzzy delivery contains a cuddly surprise for Baby Box. In the dollhouse, Gabby and Pandy attempt to keep up with some cute and crafty critters.

episodes.name: Kitty School
episodes.overview: As Floyd settles in for a tasty treat, Gabby grabs a new piece of mail from the Meow Meow Mailbox and prepares for an action-packed day at kitty school.

episodes.name: Kitty Cat Cam
episodes.overview: Fun is only a snapshot away as Gabby and Pandy set out to take a group photo — and make time for a picture-perfect scavenger hunt!

episodes.name: Dollhouse Defenders
episodes.overview: Super Gabby and Super Pandy shrink down to save the day from a mischievous CatRat. Can they solve his playful puzzles? Let the marvelous missions begin!

episodes.name: Mixed-Up Dollhouse
episodes.overview: A sparkly Meow Meow Mailbox surprise leads to a mysterious dollhouse mix-up. Can Gabby and the kitties find a fix... and some bubbly fun?

episodes.name: Game Show
episodes.overview: Ready. Set. Compete! CatRat takes center stage and hosts a series of dazzling dollhouse games. Will the crew win enough tickets to take home prizes?

episodes.name: Kitty Pirates
episodes.overview: Gabby and Pandy delight in a day of pirate-themed adventures, featuring music, maps and magical travel. Cakey leads a tasty treat tutorial.

episodes.name: MerCat Gets Her Sparkle Back
episodes.overview: Mush, mash and mix in a dash! Gabby and her friends prepare for a spa day. Meanwhile, MerCat deals with a sparkle disaster. Can the gang find a fix?

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: Cute cats, quirky crafts and colorful magic! Join kitty enthusiast Gabby and her sidekick Pandy Paws as they team up for a series of animated adventures.

episodes.name: Itty Bitty Blossom
episodes.overview: A darling delivery leads to a garden adventure when Gabby and Pandy call on Kitty Fairy and crew to help grow and soothe an itty bitty blossom.

episodes.name: Dollhouse Store Day
episodes.overview: It’s almost time to get groovy at the music store grand opening! Can Gabby and Pandy earn enough kitty coins to buy an instrument?

episodes.name: Kitty Fairy’s Sleepover
episodes.overview: As Floyd snuggles up for bedtime, Gabby, Pandy and Pillow Cat prepare for a sleepover in Kitty Fairy’s garden, complete with a magical pajama tree.

episodes.name: Let's Make a Movie!
episodes.overview: Lights, camera, CatRat! Gabby and the gang help turn a beloved fairy tale into a movie and get crafty with costumes, props and sound effects.

episodes.name: Pete the Polar Bear
episodes.overview: A frosty friend from the North Pole pays a visit to the dollhouse and learns all about the splish-splash spirit on his very first beach day.

episodes.name: Kitty Rangers
episodes.overview: Gabby and Pandy receive special sashes and start their journey as kitty rangers! Can they use their new skills to solve a missing mama mystery?

episodes.name: The Meow-Mazing Games
episodes.overview: Get ready to race, jump and fly as Gabby, Pandy, Carlita and the DooDads compete for a big, beautiful Meow-Mazing Games trophy!

episodes.name: Pandy's Birthday
episodes.overview: Next stop: Birthday Island! In honor of Pandy’s big day, Gabby prepares a heartfelt gift, and the dollhouse friends celebrate with a series of surprises.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: More paws-itively purr-fect fun awaits as Gabby and her dollhouse friends find new ways to learn, create and celebrate in a whimsical world of joy.

episodes.name: The Dollhouse Hotel
episodes.overview: A tiny suitcase surprise leads to a fancy hotel stay for Gabby and Pandy, featuring "cat-abulous" spa treatments and a popping pool party.

episodes.name: A Knight’s Tail
episodes.overview: Gabby and Pandy become knights in training and practice bravery by crossing a moat, mixing potions and more.

episodes.name: DJ's Glow Ride
episodes.overview: It's time to light up the night with a glow-in-the-dark delivery; Gabby, Pandy and DJ Catnip get to work on a train-building project.

episodes.name: Rainy Day Banana
episodes.overview: Inspired by a sparkly banana, Gabby and her friends make the most of a rainy day in the dollhouse and craft songs and snacks.

episodes.name: CatRat the Bandit
episodes.overview: Gabby and Pandy say "howdy" to a cowboy adventure as they hit trails and rails to protect a pouch of golden nuggets from CatRat.

episodes.name: DJ Catnip Gets His Groove Back
episodes.overview: Gabby, Pandy and DJ Catnip are ready to make music and search high and low for moving and grooving sounds.

episodes.name: Kitty Fairy Gets Sick
episodes.overview: After Kitty Fairy catches a cold, Gabby and Pandy deliver dandelion soup and step in to save the day.

3.name: Season 3
3.overview: Gabby, Pandy and their crew of kitty friends are back with even more special deliveries, surprising journeys and make-at-home lessons, too!

episodes.name: Cakey’s Cupcake Cousins
episodes.overview: It's cousin time; Bakey, Flakey, Marshapan, and Paddycake visit Cakey and the dollhouse gang for a "sprinkle-rific" day of yummy snacks and hug attacks.

episodes.name: It’s Purrsday!
episodes.overview: Gabby and friends go all out for an extra special holiday, throwing a "paw-tastic" party, complete with homemade decorations and dessert.

episodes.name: Dollhouse Safari
episodes.overview: Gabby, Pandy and their curious crew set out on an animal safari to find a mysterious creature.

episodes.name: Fluffy Flufferton
episodes.overview: Glittery and glamorous Fluffy Flufferton is the most "a-meowzing" pop star; the gang helps her shake things up before a big concert.

episodes.name: Abra-CAT-Dabra!
episodes.overview: A tiny top hat delivery leads to a dazzling day for new magician Baby Box; meanwhile, her closest friends help her perform a boppin'-and-hoppin' trick.

episodes.name: The Fairy Festival!
episodes.overview: It's fairy o'clock and the start of a fantastic festival, featuring rides, games, cotton candy, and a new friend with a flower contest dream.

episodes.name: Dollhouse FairyTales
episodes.overview: Tall tales come to life with a king, a mermaid and so much more as Gabby and the gang create and celebrate enchanting fairytales in a storybook castle.

episodes.name: The Easter Kitty Bunny
episodes.overview: Gabby and Pandy practise patience as they wait for a super cute egg to hatch; luckily, Kitty Fairy, MerCat and DJ Catnip are there to lend helping paws.

4.name: Season 4
4.overview: New lessons, new surprises, same adorable kitties — including Floyd! Gabby leads the way with Pandy, CatRat, Cakey, Baby Box and other beloved pals.

episodes.name: Gabby, I Shrunk the Kitties!
episodes.overview: When Gabby and Pandy turn tiny from one of MerCat's potions, they'll need to gather the right ingredients to help them grow back to their usual size.

episodes.name: Mission to CATurn
episodes.overview: Gabby and Pandy blast off to Planet Caturn after CatRat gets stuck there looking for space cheese.

episodes.name: Doodlebook
episodes.overview: Gabby finds a book with the same doodle on every page; inside the dollhouse, the Gabby Cats use their imagination to add their own spin to the drawings.

episodes.name: Cupcake Tree
episodes.overview: Cupcake expert Cakey helps Gabby and Pandy shrink down a giant cupcake tree to rescue CatRat and the Gabby Cats from its overgrown branches.

episodes.name: Dollhouse Detectives
episodes.overview: Gabby and Pandy play detectives when things start to suddenly and mysteriously disappear around the dollhouse.

episodes.name: Happy CAT-O-Ween!
episodes.overview: Everyone's in the Cat-O-Ween spirit; Gabby and Pandy make cat-o-lanterns with Baby Box, search for treats with MerCat, and make banana ghosts with Cakey.

5.name: Season 5
5.overview: From the Cat-osphere to Cat-O-Ween, Gabby, Pandy and pals mix their kitty magic and curiosity together to discover new adventures and ways to play!

episodes.name: A CAT-Tabulous Christmas
episodes.overview: Meow-y Christmas! Gabby and Pandy have some Christmas wishes — but first they need to help Figgy the Elf learn from her present-wrapping mistakes.

episodes.name: CatRat's Puzzle Hunt
episodes.overview: CatRat takes Gabby and Pandy on a puzzle hunt through the dollhouse, where they solve riddles, play games and find fun surprises along the way.

episodes.name: Super Thinkers!
episodes.overview: While completing an obstacle course to become superheroes, Gabby and Pandy learn how to use their bodies — as well as their minds!

episodes.name: Paper Cup Popper
episodes.overview: After Gabby finds a box of paper cups, the friends get creative making paper cup animal crafts, telling stories and playing fur-tastic games.

episodes.name: Dollhouse Dress-Up Chest
episodes.overview: Gabby uses the power of dress-up to travel to the Wild West, outer space and even underwater to help solve her friends' problems.

episodes.name: Kico the KittyCorn
episodes.overview: On a rainy day, Gabby and friends must take care of Kico — a baby KittyCorn who's part kitty, part unicorn — until it's time for her to meet her family.

6.name: Season 6
6.overview: Join Gabby, Pandy and their kitty pals for more creative adventures in their magical dollhouse, where they play dress-up, become superheroes and more!

episodes.name: Planes, Trains, and Kitty Balloons!
episodes.overview: Gabby and Pandy take a travel adventure using a train, plane, cruise ship and hot air balloon — but they can't forget to take pictures for CatRat.

episodes.name: True Fairy Friends
episodes.overview: A glowing lantern leads Gabby and Pandy to a Fairy Fly House! But to meet their new neighbor, they'll need to prove they're helpful, kind and welcoming.

episodes.name: Googly Eyes
episodes.overview: When Gabby and Pandy find a magical jar of googly eyes, they're in for a troublemaking surprise. Luckily MerCat knows just how to burst trouble's bubble.

episodes.name: Spongey-Saurus
episodes.overview: Roar! Stomp! When Spongey-Saurus gets wet, he grows. When he dries out, he shrinks. Can Gabby and Pandy keep their new dino-pal the perfect size?

episodes.name: Baby Box’s Meow-Seum Day!
episodes.overview: The Gabby Cats need to make a special art project for Baby Box's Meow-Seum Day. But with many different ways to make art, who knows what they'll create!

episodes.name: Carlita the Ice Cream Truck!
episodes.overview: Carlita has transformed into an ice cream truck! Before she can deliver sweet treats to all the Gabby Cats, she'll need ice cream, a menu and a song.

7.name: Season 7
7.overview: Gabby and her best pal Pandy Paws meet fairies, find treasure and go on wild adventures inside her super-special dollhouse. Come play and sing along!

episodes.name: The Magical Mermaid-Lantis
episodes.overview: SunnyCat invites Gabby to a Mermaid Sparkle Party in Mermaid-Lantis! But to attend, she needs to bring MerCat's blue crystal — and her special sparkle.

episodes.name: Snow Cruise
episodes.overview: Gabby and Pandy learn all about snow science when they take a cruise to the North Pole to see a rainbow igloo that Pete the Polar Bear and CatRat built.

episodes.name: Baby Benny Box Is Here!
episodes.overview: The Box Family welcomes its newest member: Benny Box! When Mama Box needs a nap, Gabby and Pandy teach Baby Box how to babysit her new brother.

episodes.name: The Mermaid Cruise Ship
episodes.overview: Gabby's going on a mermaid cruise! There are a ton of fun activities to do aboard the ship, like making mer-mazing crowns, tails and treats.

episodes.name: Charm Bracelet Treasure Hunt
episodes.overview: Gabby and Pandy follow clues and solve riddles to find sparkly treasures on an a-meow-zing Dollhouse Treasure Hunt. Can they find all three?

episodes.name: CatRat’s KittyFish
episodes.overview: When Gabby receives a fishbowl in her Meow Meow Mailbox, CatRat wants to use it as a home for his itty bitty kittyfish. But they keep hiding!

episodes.name: The Mermaid Christmas Cruise
episodes.overview: Santa Kitty is on his way to the Mermaid Christmas Cruise to give the first present of the year to MerCat's baby sister Hsiu Hsiu — and we're invited!

8.name: Season 8
8.overview: With all new songs and all new friends, the fun times never end for Gabby and her cute cat, Pandy Paws. Want to come along? It's time to get tiny!

episodes.name: Music Festival
episodes.overview: When Gabby and Pandy score party passes to DJ Catnip's music festival, they board a groovy bus to watch shows featuring all their favorite Gabby Cats.

episodes.name: Cakey's Birthday
episodes.overview: Cakey runs out of sprinkles on the most sprinkle-riffic day of the year: his birthday! Can Cakey's friends figure out a way to bring his sprinkles back?

episodes.name: Pandy's Bad Day
episodes.overview: After messing up his hug attack and getting a hole in his Pandy Pack, Pandy realizes he's having a bad day — but things just keep getting worse.

episodes.name: Baby Box's Crafty-riffic Adventure
episodes.overview: Gabby receives a Crafty-riffic Adventure Kit in her Dollhouse Delivery, which comes in handy when CatRat spends the day crafting silly bad guys.

episodes.name: Silly Kitty Cubes
episodes.overview: Gabby brings her Silly Kitty Cubes with her to the dollhouse, where all the Gabby Cats play along by making up fun stories based on what they've rolled.

episodes.name: Carlita's Ameowzing Race
episodes.overview: It's the day of Carlita's A-meow-zing Race! After choosing their racers, Gabby and her friends speed around solving puzzles to win a special surprise.

9.name: Season 9
9.overview: With a pinch on her left and a pinch on her right, Gabby shrinks down for more kitty adventures in her super-cool dollhouse. Come and play along!

episodes.name: Happy Birthday, Gabby!
episodes.overview: CatRat wants to plan a party for Gabby's birthday, but Gabby can't decide on a theme. Will she make up her mind in time for his big surprise?

episodes.name: Marty the Party Cat
episodes.overview: There's a new Gabby Cat in town: Marty the Party Cat! Gabby and Pandy show Marty all the fun features in the party room to make him feel welcome.

episodes.name: You Wish!
episodes.overview: Gabby gets a wishing fountain and helps make the kitties' wishes come true, but Pandy can't decide what he wants — until CatRat gets into a pickle!

episodes.name: CatRat's Birthday Surprise
episodes.overview: It's CatRat's birthday! Help Gabby and the gang plan a super-secret surprise party for their feline friend and his very special guest, Fluffy Flufferton.

episodes.name: Craft Bot
episodes.overview: Baby Box's Kitty Bots cause confusion in the dollhouse when they wind up in the wrong rooms. Can you help the cat pals find where the robots belong?

episodes.name: Grandma CatRat
episodes.overview: CatRat wants everything to be perfect for his grandma's visit. But when things don't go as planned, the day is full of new and exciting surprises.

10.name: Season 10
10.overview: Come celebrate special holidays with Gabby and her friends, from a birthday to Family Day to Opposite Day. Every day is a celebration at the Dollhouse!
